description: Major price adjustment! Located in the heart of South Boston, this luxurious corner unit epitomizes modern comfort and style.Featuring 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms & parking! This home is designed for upscale living. Enjoy the elegance of 8-foot doors, tall ceilings and hardwood floors,complemented by oversized Pella windows that fill the space with natural light.The chef’s kitchen is a culinary dream, equipped with stainless-steel Jenn-Air appliances,custom Wolf cabinetry, & Calacatta Quartz countertops with a spacious island perfect for entertaining .The bathrooms offer a touch of luxury with custom tiles and floating vanities. Additional features include in-unit laundry, hydro central air system,audiovisual intercom, and a private balcony. Modern conveniences like a Nest thermostat, pre-wired surround sound, heated garage parking, 24/7 off-site professional management to enhance the lifestyle. Located minutes from W Broadway Station, Capo, Lincoln, Carson & M St beach!
